or ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</author><title level="m">Briefwechsel, Aufzeichnungen, Dokumente (1891–1931)</title><editor>Hg. Kurt Ifkovits und Martin Anton Müller</editor><imprint><pubPlace>Göttingen</pubPlace><publisher>Wallstein</publisher><date when="2018">2018</date></imprint></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb10815">Bahr, Hermann</persName><placeName ref="#pmb986">Lindau</placeName><date when="1908-11-10" n="01">10. 11. 1908</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10815">Bahr, Hermann</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1908-11-09_02">Probst, Probst, Staehelin-Baechtold, Huber, Staehelin-Baechtold, Kesser, , Bodmer, Bodman, Sartoris, Sartoris, Bodmer, Bahr an Schnitzler, 9. 11. 1908</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1908-11-15_01">Schnitzler an Bahr, 15. 11. 1908</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, e.g. @type="schnitzlerDiary" @target="1891-05-15". The complete URI is: 'https://schnitzler-tagebuch.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/v/editions/entry__1891-05-15'</ab></refsDecl></encodingDesc><revisionDesc status="approved"><change who="KI MAM" when="2015-12-16">Kollationiert</change><change who="KI MAM" when="2017-05-30">Kollationiert</change><change who="MAM" when="2018-07-15">Überführt aus Bahr–Schnitzler-Daten</change><change who="MAM" when="2019-01-20">Index check</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><graphic url="MS-B-00005-B-000-00284"/><graphic url="MS-B-00005-B-000-00285"/></facsimile><text type="card"><body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00284"/>Artur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb133" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><date>10. 11.</date></dateline></opener><p>Ich habe Dich am<date>5.</date>in<rs ref="#pmb146" type="place">Frankfurt</rs>und gestern<anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL322-1"/>in<rs ref="#pmb484" type="place">Zürich</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL322-1h">Zur Lesung am<date>9. 11. 1908</date>im<rs ref="#pmb29322" type="org">Lesezirkel Hottingen</rs>ist sowohl in<rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahrs</rs>wie auch in<rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzlers</rs>Papieren (<bibl>University of Exeter,<publisher>The Schnitzler Press-Cuttings Archive</publisher>, Box 1/6</bibl>) das Programmheft überliefert. Als Ablauf wird angegeben: »<quote>1. Über<rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs>2.<rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzlers</rs>Novelle: ›<rs ref="#pmb29833" type="work">Die Toten schweigen</rs>‹</quote>«.</note>besungen,<add place="above">über</add>morgen wirst Dus auch noch nicht in<rs ref="#pmb881" type="place">Mannheim</rs>. Verschaff Dir das letzte Heft des »<rs ref="#pmb34262" type="work">Morgen</rs>«, wo ich<rs type="work" ref="#pmb30089" subtype="implied">einiges</rs>zum »<rs ref="#pmb29923" type="work">Weg ins Freie</rs>« gesagt habe.</p><closer>Mit vielen Grüßen an Deine liebe<rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs><lb/>herzlichst<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed></closer></div></body></text></TEI>